social_posts.post_text: I’ve got something exciting to share with y’all today. Check out my story!😌

You live in integrity, listen enthusiastically, and embody the duality of vulnerability and strength. You’re brilliant, deliberately considerate, oddly resourceful, and intentionally optimistic. A conglomeration of all things genuine and kind; I look up to you in so many ways. Sure life is inherently precious, but with you, I slow down enough to notice. Happy birthday to the man of my dreams, who doubles as a real life pirate. ⛵️🔭🐸❤️‍🔥🏴‍☠️🌙🦜
Getting by with a little help from my friends 🫶
